# Post content (i.e.: the stuff on the post's page)
All of your content should be written using markdown. That makes it
super easy to write *and* super easy to convert into proper HTML.
One more note: please follow the structure of this raw post exactly.
Basically, that means: title is the first line, description is the
second line, all tags on the third line, and content (in markdown)
from the fourth line onwards. Just make sure you watch that return
key, chump, and we won't have any problems ;-)
